{"tid":768121,"cid":21,"subCid":3,"title":"有冇人覺得槙原敬之係一個好離譜嘅人？","createTime":"2018-08-05T06:22:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-06T19:04:58.000Z","uid":93046,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3870181898982f1be5ad29990b79e642331a9f88","tid":768121,"uid":93046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T06:22:58.000Z","msg":"神得好離譜<br />\n出道差唔多30年<br />\n啲歌全部自己都作曲作詞<br />\n主打歌，非主打歌好多都好聽<br />\n創造好多經典<br />\n1991年首三月的雪係我嘅最愛<br />\n<br />\n佢把聲又靚又獨特<br />\n聽到人好舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢好多歌我都好鍾意"},{"pid":"1bd8396111082aa01e1557e3233d7b564f5a6b97","tid":768121,"uid":79120,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T15:47:38.000Z","msg":"90年代佢真係好紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nどんなときも<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/b88pxLpMZKk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fb88pxLpMZKk&d=02GaBAoxlhcSD3HkkvnXHsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=72afd4c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/b88pxLpMZKk</a><br />\n<br />\n其實日本幾多歌手係自己作曲作詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9937b26441c8c6bdc6f5f21c3b64adc7dfd5ce34","tid":768121,"uid":93046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1bd8396111082aa01e1557e3233d7b564f5a6b97","tid":768121,"uid":79120,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T15:47:38.000Z","msg":"90年代佢真係好紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nどんなときも<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/b88pxLpMZKk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fb88pxLpMZKk&d=02GaBAoxlhcSD3HkkvnXHsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk